Gridworld Remap & 81.67\% success & 0.0\% & 0.0 & Yes & 3/3 ablations \\
Sequential Rules & 84.67\% accuracy & 2.45\% & 0.021 & Yes & 3/3
ablations \\
\bottomrule()
